# Stage 1: Build frontend with Node.js
FROM node:20-alpine AS frontend-builder

WORKDIR /app/frontend

COPY frontend/package*.json ./

RUN npm ci && npm run build


# Stage 2: Python runtime
FROM python:3.12-slim

WORKDIR /app

RUN apt-get update && \
    apt-get install --no-install-recommends -y libpq-dev unixodbc-dev curl && \
    apt-get clean && \
    rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

RUN useradd -u 1000 -m superset

COPY --chown=superset:superset pyproject.toml poetry.lock ./

RUN pip install --no-cache-dir poetry && \
    poetry config virtualenvs.create true && \
    poetry config virtualenvs.in-project true && \
    poetry install --no-root

COPY --chown=superset:superset .venv /app/.venv
COPY --chown=superset:superset backend /app/backend
COPY --from=frontend-builder --chown=superset:superset /app/frontend/dist /app/static

ENV PATH="/app/.venv/bin:$PATH"

USER superset

EXPOSE 8088

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:8088/health || exit 1

LABEL maintainer="team@example.com" \
      description="Python analytics platform with React frontend"

CMD ["gunicorn", "-w", "4", "-b", "0.0.0.0:8088", "app:create_app()"]
